title: EP.43: NBA TRADES, USC/UCLA LEAVING THE PAC12, TRIVIA, NFL BIGGEST MOVERS, AND MUCH MORE!
description: In this episode we talk about the trades and trade rumors currently circling the NBA and also talk about why USC and UCLA should stay in the PAC12. Joe answers some trivia questions and we talk about which NFL team has the most potential to go from worst to first.... or at least to mid
